  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Events Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>Are you passionate about coffee and enjoy working in dynamic event environments? Kings Cart Coffee is looking for an enthusiastic <strong>Events Assistant</strong> to join our team! In this role, you will play a key part in setting up and managing coffee cart events and ensuring smooth deliveries. If you have barista experience and a valid driving license, this could be the perfect opportunity for you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Set up and break down coffee cart equipment at events.</li>\n  <li>Handle coffee making and customer service during events.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely and safe delivery of coffee beans and equipment to event locations.</li>\n  <li>Assist in event coordination and provide support to the team as needed.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and proper upkeep of equipment during and after events.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Barista experience</strong> is highly preferred.</li>\n  <li>Valid <strong>Class 3/3A driving license</strong> is a must.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and customer service skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work flexible hours, including weekends and public holidays.</li>\n  <li>Physically able to lift and transport equipment up to 30KG.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 day work week</li>\n  <li>Staff Discount</li>\n  <li>Birthday Leave</li>\n  <li>Medical Benefits</li>\n  <li>Bi-Annual Bonus</li>\n  <li>Training and Uniform provided</li>\n  <li>Skill development and career progression opportunities</li>\n  <li>$1200 New Join Bonus Incentive (T&amp;C applies)</li>\n</ul>",
