    "description": "<p>Our team is operating under the brand King’s Cart Coffee. It is overseeing 4 different areas in</p>\n<p>(1) Wholesale Coffee Roasting &amp; Supply</p>\n<p>(2) Events (Coffee Carts)</p>\n<p>(3) In-house Barista to Large Corporations</p>\n<p>(4) Café and Retail (eg. Kings Cart Coffee Factory)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are expanding our 4th pallet and would like to invite you to be part of our growth!</p>",
